  "logNo": "110174284953",
  "title": "노을캠핑장 1박2일 8/14~15",
  "addDate": "2013. 8. 16.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110174284953",
  "html_size": 193850,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110174284953\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110174284953\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"3028548_9\"; font-size: 9pt;'> \r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>다시 노을캠핑장을 방문합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>여전히 짐을 내리고 옮기고 맹꽁이차에 싣고, 내리고 카트로 옮기고 등등의 과정은 힘드네요 ^^;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>그래도 맹꽁이차 타고 캠핑장으로 올라가는 길은 신선한 바람과 설래는 마음이 있네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a2e7612f760d7292.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_30/isuhani_13766541458212MESK_JPEG/IMG_4112.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a2e7612f760d7292.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_151/isuhani_1376654146142x0zjC_JPEG/IMG_4121.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_151/isuhani_1376654146142x0zjC_JPEG/IMG_4121.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_151/isuhani_1376654146142x0zjC_JPEG/IMG_4121.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_38/isuhani_13766541463661C6LQ_JPEG/IMG_4159.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_38/isuhani_13766541463661C6LQ_JPEG/IMG_4159.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_38/isuhani_13766541463661C6LQ_JPEG/IMG_4159.JPG?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>날씨. 정말 좋아요! </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>덥기도 무척 더워요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>하지만 하루종일 에어컨바람 속에서 살다보니</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>이런 더위가 반갑고 고맙네요 ^^</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_156/isuhani_1376654292303GWX5V_JPEG/IMG_4123.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_156/isuhani_1376654292303GWX5V_JPEG/IMG_4123.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_156/isuhani_1376654292303GWX5V_JPEG/IMG_4123.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>이번에는 알록달록 시피너와 바람개비도 설치해봅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>싸게 판다고 해서 덥썩 샀는데 ㅎㅎㅎ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>애들이 1분 정도 관심을 가져주더니 더이상 관심이 없네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_75/isuhani_1376654292651lA0Xe_JPEG/IMG_4124.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_75/isuhani_1376654292651lA0Xe_JPEG/IMG_4124.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_75/isuhani_1376654292651lA0Xe_JPEG/IMG_4124.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>아들은 장작으로 길을 만들고 집을 짓는다고 땀 뻘뻘 흘립니다.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_184/isuhani_13766542929315fhJO_JPEG/IMG_4127.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_184/isuhani_13766542929315fhJO_JPEG/IMG_4127.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_184/isuhani_13766542929315fhJO_JPEG/IMG_4127.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>딸은. 공주죠. </p>\r\n<p>편하게 앉아서 음료수 마시며 쉽니다. ㅎㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>남자와 여자의 차이가 </p>\r\n<p>이 어린 남매에게서도 고스란히 보이네요 </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_23/isuhani_1376654293530FxpsH_JPEG/IMG_4131.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_23/isuhani_1376654293530FxpsH_JPEG/IMG_4131.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_23/isuhani_1376654293530FxpsH_JPEG/IMG_4131.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>더운데 땀흘리며 놀았으니 </p>\r\n<p>얼음 과자가 필요합니다. </p>\r\n<p>득템!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_242/isuhani_1376654293723QlY8y_JPEG/IMG_4135.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_242/isuhani_1376654293723QlY8y_JPEG/IMG_4135.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_242/isuhani_1376654293723QlY8y_JPEG/IMG_4135.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>물 떠놓고 썬크림 바르는 거라며 열심히 양 팔에 바르고 있네요 ^^;;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_187/isuhani_1376654293903qYzYx_JPEG/IMG_4143.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_187/isuhani_1376654293903qYzYx_JPEG/IMG_4143.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_187/isuhani_1376654293903qYzYx_JPEG/IMG_4143.JPG?type=w3\"></div>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>무더위에도 불은 피웁니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>제 머리속에는 '캠프 파이어'에 대한 긍정적 기억이 강하게 각인되어있나 봅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>불이 사그러들어야 고기를 구울 수 있으니 그 시간동안 기다립니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_18/isuhani_1376654760768XdRHc_JPEG/IMG_4149.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_18/isuhani_1376654760768XdRHc_JPEG/IMG_4149.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_18/isuhani_1376654760768XdRHc_JPEG/IMG_4149.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>기다리는 동안 랜턴을 켜고 그림놀이를 합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>스케치북과 크레파스만 있다면 기다리는 시간은 지루하지 않죠.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_38/isuhani_1376654761153kojAf_JPEG/IMG_4153.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_38/isuhani_1376654761153kojAf_JPEG/IMG_4153.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_38/isuhani_1376654761153kojAf_JPEG/IMG_4153.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>고기와 새우를 구워봅니다. </p>\r\n<p>든든히 먹어야 내일 철수할 때 힘을 쓸 수 있어요. </p>\r\n<p>아침은. 부실하게 먹게될 테니까요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_129/isuhani_1376654761556lUt6u_JPEG/IMG_4161.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_129/isuhani_1376654761556lUt6u_JPEG/IMG_4161.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_129/isuhani_1376654761556lUt6u_JPEG/IMG_4161.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>다음날. </p>\r\n<p>광복절입니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>날씨가 너무 좋네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_32/isuhani_1376654761867cDvOM_JPEG/IMG_4162.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_32/isuhani_1376654761867cDvOM_JPEG/IMG_4162.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_32/isuhani_1376654761867cDvOM_JPEG/IMG_4162.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>멀리 산도 보이고</p>\r\n<p>(북한산 ?&nbsp;도봉산 ?)</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_213/isuhani_13766547622742bNE0_JPEG/IMG_4166.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_213/isuhani_13766547622742bNE0_JPEG/IMG_4166.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_213/isuhani_13766547622742bNE0_JPEG/IMG_4166.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>자연놀이터. </p>\r\n<p>나무블럭, 나무공, 미로찾기, 터널 등등등</p>\r\n<p>땡볕에 시간가는줄 모르고 놉니다. </p>\r\n<p>땀 뻘뻘 흘리면서 말이죠. 엄마가 지켜보느라 고생입니다. </p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1f80092426c95f02.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_116/isuhani_1376654762517x3Gl9_JPEG/IMG_4191.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1f80092426c95f02.jpg\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\"아이스크림 사줄테니 매점가자\"</p>\r\n<p>고 </p>\r\n<p>꼬셔서 겨우 놀이터를 벗어납니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이젠, 집에 가야지!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fef3f84352ab3b02.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_197/isuhani_1376654762839qMQkh_JPEG/IMG_4197.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fef3f84352ab3b02.jpg\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>둘째는. 지쳐 잠이 들었네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_283/isuhani_1376654763230K78fT_JPEG/IMG_4208.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 493px; rwidth: 740px;\" id=\"20130816_283/isuhani_1376654763230K78fT_JPEG/IMG_4208.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6E62C99')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130816_283/isuhani_1376654763230K78fT_JPEG/IMG_4208.JPG?type=w3\"></div>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>내려가는 맹꽁이차를 기다리면서 관리사무실을 찍어봅니다.. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>노을캠핑장은 푸르름 만으로도 너무 맘에 듭니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>애들도 좋아하네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>다음에 또 오자고 얘기합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>그러나, 15일 2시에&nbsp;9월&nbsp;예약이 오픈이니까..&nbsp; (노을캠핑장에서 내려오는 시간이 2시즈음 되었네요)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>우리는 9월 주말 예약은 물건너갔단다 ^^;;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>가능한 날 예약하기가 너무 어려워요~</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>이용객들이 예약해놓고 못오고 된 경우에는 예약을 취소해주면 좋겠어요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'>예약취소해주면 다른 가족들이라도 갈 수 있으니까요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style='font-family: \"957317_10\"; font-size: 10pt;'></span>&nbsp;</p></div>\r\n </div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
